trans-unit.source: Defines the base class for resources that can be added to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Definierar basklass för resurser som kan läggas till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Commits all changes and flushes the resource to the document package.
trans-unit.target: Genomför alla ändringar och rensningar resursen till dokumentet paketet.

trans-unit.source: Based on settings of <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>, such as <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>, the flush operation of the Commit method may be delayed until the whole <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> is closed.
trans-unit.target: Baserat på inställningarna för <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>och <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>, som <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies>och <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>, streamsqlstore av Commit-metoden kan vara fördröjd förrän hela <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>är stängd.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns the I/O stream for reading or writing the resource.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar i/o-dataströmmen för läsning eller skrivning resursen när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.Stream> for reading or writing the resource.
Returns the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the resource that is relative to a specified absolute [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] på den resurs som är relativ till en angiven absoluta [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The of the resource that is relative to the specified absolute inUri.
trans-unit.target: Den på den resurs som är i förhållande till det angivna absolut inUri .

trans-unit.source: This member supports the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
